metadata.name: The Duck
metadata.description: Introducing an NFT of a Japanese 18th century-style duck. This unique digital art piece features a colorful and intricate depiction of a duck in a natural setting with cherry blossom trees in the background. Every feather is beautifully detailed, capturing the essence of Japanese art. This NFT is perfect for art lovers and collectors looking for a one-of-a-kind piece of digital art.
